<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact - Arcane Archives</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="esoteric-bg"></div>
    
    <!-- Floating Esoteric Symbols -->
    <div class="floating-symbol" style="top: 10%; left: 5%;">☿</div>
    <div class="floating-symbol" style="top: 20%; left: 85%; animation-delay: -5s;">♀</div>
    <div class="floating-symbol" style="top: 60%; left: 10%; animation-delay: -10s;">♃</div>
    <div class="floating-symbol" style="top: 80%; left: 80%; animation-delay: -15s;">♄</div>
    
    <header>
        <div class="logo">ARCANE ARCHIVES</div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/library" class="nav-link">Forbidden Library</a></li>
                <li><a href="/societies" class="nav-link">Secret Societies</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact" class="nav-link active">Contact</a></li>
                <li><a href="/upload-book" class="nav-link">Upload Books</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    
    <main>
        <h1>Seek Further Knowledge</h1>
        <p>If you wish to delve deeper into these mysteries or have discovered esoteric knowledge of your own, you may contact the archivists. Be warned: not all inquiries receive responses, and those that do may not provide the answers you expect.</p>
        
        <div class="contact-form">
            <form id="esoteric-contact">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name">Your Arcane Designation</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Scrying Mirror Address</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="subject">Nature of Inquiry</label>
                    <select id="subject" name="subject" required>
                        <option value="">Select a topic...</option>
                        <option value="alchemy">Alchemical Processes</option>
                        <option value="hermetic">Hermetic Principles</option>
                        <option value="qabalah">Qabbalistic Paths</option>
                        <option value="societies">Secret Societies</option>
                        <option value="other">Other Esoteric Matter</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="message">Your Query</label>
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" required></textarea>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>
                        <input type="checkbox" name="initiate" required>
                        I understand that pursuing forbidden knowledge carries inherent risks to my perception of reality.
                    </label>
                </div>
                
                <button type="submit">Send Through the Ether</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        
        <p class="warning">By contacting us, you acknowledge that the Arcane Archives assumes no responsibility for any shifts in consciousness, paradigm collapses, or existential crises that may result from engaging with the materials provided.</p>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
        <p>Arcane Archives &copy; <span id="current-year"></span> | Knowledge Forbidden to the Uninitiated</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>